<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <a href="/become-instructor/step3" class="back-btn">
  <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-left"></i>
  Back to Instructor Application
</a>
  <title>Instructor Terms & Conditions - TheDevStudio</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.0/css/all.min.css"/>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/base.css" />
  <style>
    .terms-container {
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 80px auto;
      padding: 48px;
      background: var(--surface);
      border-radius: 16px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .terms-title {
      font-size: 36px;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: var(--text-white);
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .terms-date {
      color: var(--text-muted);
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }
    .terms-section {
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }
    .terms-section h2 {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--text-white);
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .terms-section p, .terms-section li {
      color: var(--text-body);
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .terms-section ul {
      padding-left: 24px;
    }
     .back-btn {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 8px;
      width: fit-content;
      margin: 48px auto 24px;
      color: var(--pink);
      font-weight: 700;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .back-btn:hover {
      color: var(--pink-light);
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('../partials/navbar') %>
  
  <div class="terms-container">
    <h1 class="terms-title">Instructor Terms & Conditions</h1>
    <p class="terms-date">Effective Date: January 1, 2025</p>
    
    <div class="terms-section">
      <h2>1. Instructor Responsibilities</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>All course content must be original or properly licensed</li>
        <li>Instructors must respond to student questions within 48 hours</li>
        <li>Courses must meet platform quality standards before publishing</li>
        <li>Instructors agree to maintain professional conduct at all times</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    
    <div class="terms-section">
      <h2>2. Content Guidelines</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>No harmful, offensive, or misleading material is permitted</li>
        <li>Content must be educational and provide value to students</li>
        <li>Copyright infringement will result in immediate account suspension</li>
        <li>TheDevStudio reserves the right to remove courses that violate guidelines</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    
    <div class="terms-section">
      <h2>3. Revenue & Payments</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Revenue share: Instructors receive 70% of course sales after platform fees</li>
        <li>Payments are processed monthly for earnings above $50</li>
        <li>Student refunds may reduce instructor earnings within 30 days of purchase</li>
        <li>TheDevStudio handles all payment processing and student billing</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    
    <div class="terms-section">
      <h2>4. Course Approval Process</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>All courses require admin approval before becoming visible to students</li>
        <li>Review typically takes 24-72 hours</li>
        <li>Courses may be rejected if they don't meet quality standards</li>
        <li>Instructors will be notified via email of approval or rejection</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    
    <div class="terms-section">
      <h2>5. Account Termination</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>TheDevStudio may terminate instructor accounts for policy violations</li>
        <li>Instructors may request account deletion at any time</li>
        <li>Upon termination, existing students retain access to purchased courses</li>
        <li>Outstanding payments will be processed within 60 days</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    
    <div class="terms-section">
      <h2>6. Contact & Support</h2>
      <p>For questions about instructor terms, contact us at <strong>support@thedevstudio.com</strong></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
